  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Little Brave is a 2D action-adventure immersive metroidvania  about a little boy Keely. Get ready for an exciting adventure. Uncover  the secrets of an old tale, gain bravery and strength on the path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/4718696a0576a67327261e74400aa3e0.poster.avif?t=1773780329\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/4718696a0576a67327261e74400aa3e0.webm?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/4718696a0576a67327261e74400aa3e0.mp4?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keely lives in a world in which a long time ago there was magic. But one day a terrible curse distorted the magical places. Keely dreams of embarking on a journey to discover the mystery of forbidden lands and the secrets of the First Wardens past. Once fate gives him such a chance...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CAREFULLY STYLIZED LOCATIONS AND TRICKY RIDDLES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tExplore the forbidden lands; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tSolve puzzles;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tOvercome treacherous traps;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/15285ca08449f2669d97050faf32bf6e.poster.avif?t=1773780329\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/15285ca08449f2669d97050faf32bf6e.webm?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/15285ca08449f2669d97050faf32bf6e.mp4?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>USEFUL SKILLS AND SOLID ENEMY AI</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tUse a combination of melee weapon, ranged attacks, and mythic magic;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against sinister enemies;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/b025ee10163cfd5a2ef9e8dc238952c6.poster.avif?t=1773780329\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/b025ee10163cfd5a2ef9e8dc238952c6.webm?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/b025ee10163cfd5a2ef9e8dc238952c6.mp4?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AN EXCITING STORY FULL OF SECRETS AND MYSTERIES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tFind the last pieces of gone magic;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tDefeat the mighty wardens;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tReveal the mystery of the legendary past;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/49c484fcfa6b2a84a3899a72e6236896.poster.avif?t=1773780329\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/49c484fcfa6b2a84a3899a72e6236896.webm?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/49c484fcfa6b2a84a3899a72e6236896.mp4?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAIN BRAVERY ON YOUR PATH</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tFind and save Weyka is a younger sister of Keely;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tSlay a monster of the forbidden lands.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/644482139a0d553bfa3da8638fc353bf.poster.avif?t=1773780329\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/644482139a0d553bfa3da8638fc353bf.webm?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724300/extras/644482139a0d553bfa3da8638fc353bf.mp4?t=1773780329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
